(ii) crawler.py
This module is responsible for exploring the target website.
Purpose
The purpose of this module is to:
Discover all accessible links


Extract HTML forms


Identify input fields


Detect GET and POST parameters


What It Does
Sends HTTP request to target URL.


Parses HTML using BeautifulSoup.


Extracts:


<a> tags (links)


<form> tags


<input> fields


